name: Delivery Rush (CloudGames)
description:
A Casual game where players rush to deliver the goods to their perspective stores, challenging other players in an online fast based game.

 The Game is Currently Playable, however more features will be added to enhance the player experience.

If you have any comment or idea to make the game better, please let us Know in the comments.
